title: Go Epic with Thule
description:
Show us the action - share the passion!

Our Thule Crew athletes need a sidekick for their next video. Upload your best video and join the competition! 

Show us your passion for snowboarding, kite surfing, biking, skiing, adventure racing, and surfing - and you can win a trip to meet and hang out with a Thule Crew member, on his/her home ground, and make a video shoot.

Upload your clip at
www.epicthule.com
